                                                                    <p>I <em>do</em> use access controls to lock down big sections, but, mostly, I handle authorization
inside my controllers.</p>
<h2 id="deny-access-the-long-way">Deny Access (the long way)! <a class="headerlink" href="deny-access-inside-controller#deny-access-the-long-way" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Let's play around: comment out the <code>access_control</code>:</p>
