<p>Head back and refresh. Access denied!</p>
<p>So what's the magic behind that <code>createAccessDeniedException()</code> method? Find out:
hold <code>Command</code> and <code>click</code> to open it. Ah, it <em>literally</em> just throws a special exception
called <code>AccessDeniedException</code>:</p>
