<h2 id="denying-access-with-annotations">Denying Access with Annotations <a class="headerlink" href="deny-access-inside-controller#denying-access-with-annotations" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>And, I have another idea! If you love annotations, you can use <em>those</em> to deny
access. Above the controller, add <code>@Security()</code> then type a little expression:
<code>is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN')</code>:</p>
