	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2982576414" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Great! That's the point I think. So you need to authenticate user on every page, for it you need to specify "pattern: ^/" in the main firewall:<br></p><pre><code><br>security:<br>    firewalls:<br>        main:<br>            pattern: ^/<br>            anonymous: true<br></code></pre><p></p><p>Do you have these lines in your firewall? Also what's in your access_control list of security.yml?</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
