	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2906396852" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2906396852" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>so, now in my security.yml:</p><p>security:<br>    role_hierarchy:<br>        ROLE_AUHTOR: [ROLE_WRITE_POST, ROLE_WRITE_COMMENT]<br>        ROLE_USER: [ROLE_WRITE_COMMENT]</p><p>(I checked here, its 4 spaces indented)</p><p>and in my twig:</p><p>{% if is_granted('ROLE_WRITE_POST') %}<br>    <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=%3AfpJuuRmGiuZLaeNqpFjCdv4J7Rs&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">New Post</a><br>{% endif %}<br>however, when I log in with a user with 'ROLE_AUTHOR', I can't see the button. <br>Just for testing,</p><p>{% if is_granted('ROLE_WRITE_POST') or is_granted('ROLE_AUTHOR') %}<br>    <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=%3AfpJuuRmGiuZLaeNqpFjCdv4J7Rs&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">New Post</a><br>{% endif %}<br>this is working fine. So, did I forget anything?</p>
